name: Who-is-SubNet.chptr_u+0004
description:
final chapter of this stage of this series, u+0004

i am further dividing my subnet. i will come visit from time to time, but i need to go out and develop new pathways and expressions to build onto this world, not just repeat what it needs back to it. i will see you on the opensea, both Near and far into the reaches of the metaverse. We may not always be in touch, but you will see my mark on the network.
